offered to pay 1 billion koruna ($56 million) for 100 percent of
the shares in Prague-based lottery company Sazka AS,  Hospodarske
Noviny  reported, citing a press release from Vitek.  Vitek, a real-estate magnate, holds about 3 billion koruna
